Exercice 3:

  <<Instruction>>	         <<Valeurs des variables>>
 q = n < p;	                q = false;
 q = n == p;	                q = false;
 q = p % n + p > n;	        q = false;
 x = p / n;	                x = 0.9;
 x = (float) p / n;	        x = 0.9;
 x = (p + 0.5) / n;	        x = 1.0;
 x = (int) (p + 0.5) / n;	x = 1;
 q = n * (p > n ? n : p);	q = 5;
 q = n * (p < n ? n : p);	q = 9;

